data.description: Appraised at $360,000. 1 Bedroom | 1 bath completely remolded home with 180-degree views of Makiki Valley and Punchbowl Mountains. The home has been beautifully remodeled in 2022 with Quartz Countertops and LVP flooring. The kitchen features a breakfast bar, dishwasher, and a quant pantry. No need for A/C, the breeze alone cools the whole home instantly. You can also step outside on the lanai and enjoy the serenity. Both the living room and bedroom have floor-to-ceiling windows with views of the Makiki Valley. The home is perfect for investors or first-time home buyers. This home is a few minutes from Ala Moana Mall, Punchbowl, University of Hawaii, and a short distance to Pearl Harbor, Hickam, Camp Smith, and Kaneohe Bay. Come stop by, take a look, and fall in love.
